EN: She decided to use disposable face masks for the convenience of cleaning the skin.

ZH: 一次性使用的纸巾通常比普通纸巾更贵。
EN: Disposable tissues are usually more expensive than regular tissues.

ZH: 这家超市不提供一次性购物袋。
EN: This supermarket does not provide disposable shopping bags.
